<p style="margin: 12px 0px 12px 0;">A career within Bank of America's Global Corporate Investment Bank group is your opportunity to:</p>
<ul>
	<li>Collaborate with client managers and product partners to understand client needs and craft solutions that address them</li>
	<li>Leverage industry expertise and deep client knowledge to offer sound financial guidance to leading companies worldwide</li>
	<li>Offer comprehensive financial services to both our issuer and investor clients - from business banking to large international corporate and institutional investors</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 12px 0px 12px 0;">
Global Corporate Investment Bank (GCIB) is all about opportunity. It's about recognizing potential, making strategic decisions, and maximizing return on investment. GCIB provides comprehensive financial solutions to clients ranging from companies with $2.5 million in revenues to large multinational corporations, governments, institutional investors, and hedge funds.
<br><br>
From bank deposit and credit services and cash management to risk management and equity and debt capital raising, we do it all. We connect investors with the most advanced debt and equity research, leading-edge sales and trading platforms, and risk management expertise - all to ensure that no opportunity for success goes unrealized.
<br><br>
As the bank of choice for 98% of the U.S. Fortune 500 and 80% of the Fortune Global 500, Bank of America is the place to be for talented professionals who are serious about seizing an opportunity to make a difference and helping to shape the future of global banking.
</p>

<h3 class="p"><span style="color: #405EBE; font-weight : bold;">Fast facts</span> about Global Corporate Investment Bank</h3>
