	<li>One in 3 midsize companies in the U.S. are clients of Bank of America</li>
	<li>In 2006, Bank of America was the fifth-largest underwriter of U.S. debt, equity, and equity-related securities</li>
	<li>Bank of America ranks No. 1 in share of both U.S. and global treasury revenues</li>
	<li>GCIB businesses also include the leading bank-owned asset-based lender and the No. 1 provider of financial services to commercial real estate businesses</li>
</ul>
